{"tid":782728,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"五夜講場 – 真係好科學 2018    量子世界","createTime":"2018-08-17T03:50:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-18T09:15:30.000Z","uid":132461,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"df2e432f8038a8c48f9748b693e3e2f13dc64476","tid":782728,"uid":132461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T03:50:38.000Z","msg":"監製：陳彩霞<br />\n<br />\n03/08/2018<br />\n當我們把物質世界聚焦到一萬億分一米的尺度時，所有現象都變得奇怪而不尋常：愈清楚粒子的位置，就愈不清楚它跑得多快；光波有粒子的性質，粒子又能像光波一樣傳播；兩顆粒子更能以超光速「瞬息傳心」，「知道」對方的狀態&hellip;&hellip;這些都超出常理和充滿不確定性，連愛因斯坦也難以置信而憤言「上帝不玩骰子遊戲！」，至今物理學家仍是「被逼」接受這些現象，未能完全參透箇中的原因。今晚就由幾位主持為大家打開薛定諤的貓盒子，迷失在撲朔迷離的量子世界吧！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n主持：<br />\n陳志宏（香港大學理學院講師）<br />\n吳家亮（香港中文大學通識教育基礎課程講師）<br />\n馬學綸（香港中文大學微生物學系博士）<br />\n陳文豪（香港教育大學科學與環境學系助理教授）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.rthk.hk/tv/dtt31/programme/sciencenight2018/episode/511373\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Ftv%2Fdtt31%2Fprogramme%2Fsciencenight2018%2Fepisode%2F511373&d=11haNinqpFo5c%2BYx51pCKwEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=f44ff304\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.rthk.hk/tv/dtt31/programme/sciencenight2018/episode/511373</a>"},{"pid":"b46effe34fa93c9eb1632a5c1a8e0f6f74079041","tid":782728,"uid":132461,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T04:07:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1a8a249c3138b4c2dae4aeba733f7413d8d50ae","tid":782728,"uid":132461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T05:08:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iVpXrbZ4bnU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DiVpXrbZ4bnU&d=11haNinqpFo5c%2BYx51pCKwEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=8418ac7e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iVpXrbZ4bnU</a>"},{"pid":"a90ade2429d99a81c185a4a4e7d2eca1383cbce4","tid":782728,"uid":132461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi